OL,6,FNexus said last week that its free
OL,7,Fspecialist adult counselling service
OL,8,Fwas to end on March 31 after it was
OL,9,Fadvised by the Department of Health
OL,10,Fthat there are no plans to replace the
OL,11,Fexisting contract.
OL,13,FHowever, answering an urgent oral
OL,14,Fquestion in the Assembly, Mr Swann
OL,15,Fsaid: "My department has been
OL,16,Fexamining potential alternative
OL,17,Farrangements following the conclusion
OL,18,Fof the Nexus contract.
