OL,6,F"A number of options have been
OL,7,Fidentified, including the provision of
OL,8,Fsupport by the community and voluntary
OL,9,Fsector, HSC trusts or primary care.
OL,11,F"However, having discussed the
OL,12,Fsituation with officials, it is clear
OL,13,Fto me that further work is required on
OL,14,Fmapping out future sustainable
OL,15,Farrangements. I have therefore
OL,16,Finstructed that the Nexus contract be
OL,17,Fextended for a further 12 months, with
OL,18,Fclose monitoring of performance
OL,19,Fthroughout that period.
